==生物構造及繁殖==
牡蠣生殖腺飽滿後，只要受外界的影響即會開始排卵、放精，像是暴風雨後的鹽分變化、滿潮露出的溫度變化等（滿月的滿潮排卵放精最多）。在水中受精後發育成浮游的[[擔輪幼蟲|擔輪幼蟲]]，待時機成熟則固著在基質上發育成帶殼的小牡蠣。牡蠣的外套膜隨者個體的成長，持續分泌建築其含有高量鈣質的外殼，保護柔軟的身體。<ref>{{cite news |title=Oyster |url=https://infovisual.info/en/biology-animal/oyster |work=The Visual Dictionary |accessdate=2018-09-08 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413003148/https://infovisual.info/en/biology-animal/oyster |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==改善海岸水質==
蠔以吃浮游生物維生，並會吸附細菌，使海水變得清潔；一隻蠔每天就能夠淨化四百公升的海水。<ref>{{cite news |title=東京灣養蠔種海藻 盼潔淨水質 |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180908/00180_031.html |work=東方日報 |date=2018-09-08 |accessdate=2018-09-08 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203211418/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180908/00180_031.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 綠牡蠣 ===
牡蠣會吸收汙染海水中的銅離子，呈現綠色的外表。

===受污染的蠔===
人類吃了受污染的蠔，有機會患病，甚至死亡。<ref>{{cite news |title=男子進食生蠔感染食肉菌死亡　食安中心：處理生蠔遭割傷或受感染 |url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2119583/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E9%80%B2%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%89%E8%8F%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E3%80%80%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E9%81%AD%E5%89%B2%E5%82%B7%E6%88%96%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93 |work=hket |date=20 July 2018 |accessdate=2018-09-08 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113040518/https://topick.hket.com/article/2119583/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E9%80%B2%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%89%E8%8F%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E3%80%80%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E9%81%AD%E5%89%B2%E5%82%B7%E6%88%96%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

